arch:property.oc:show_val: Late Paleo to St. Johns I, ca. 7500 BC to AD 100-500.
Intermittant prehistoric campsite from Late Paleo to St. Johns, 7500 BC to AD 100-500. Mid 20th century building foundation, associated with Camp Blanding military activities.
There was multiple ceramic forms from different time periods.
